                     <note><bibl>(Stegmüller, RB 6345–65 [4:280–90]), ed. PL 198:1053–1722.</bibl>
                        The final column is blank. A considerable amount of marginal addition of
                        various sorts in a variety of hands (decreases substantially after
                        Genesis).</note>
